name: svg42pdf
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "svg42pdf" %}
{% set version = "0.2.2" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/SVG42PDF-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 1f1614d52773c86d8b3cf9e0f0baf1d2e081eac3c05b01399c9f8d8c9b222b76

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - svg42pdf = svg42pdf:main
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - cairosvg
    - reportlab

test:
  imports:
    - ext.svg2rlg
    - svg42pdf
  commands:
    - svg42pdf --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/karel-brinda/svg42pdf
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Program for converting SVG to PDF.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - karel-brinda
